name: Sky Wars
description:
Sky wars is one of the most popular games in Blockman Go. 8 players will fall and land on their own island. It is important for players to search chests on their island and gather resources. Creating a bridge by blcoks to the center island will help you get better weapons and equipment. Goal of Skywars is to be the last man standing.

Want to play more interesting games?Download Blockman Go now.
